---
title: Vietnamese-Inspired Grilled Hoisin Double Pork Wraps with Mint-Cucumber Salsa, Spicy Mayo and Peanuts
description: In this fusion of flavours, sticky, hoisin-glazed pork chops are thinly sliced before getting stuffed in tortillas. The refreshing cucumber-mint salsa brightens and lightens, while the creamy spicy mayo adds some heat to every mouthwatering bite!
